cc:Work.dc:title: Triumph Spitfire MKIV colors
cc:Work.dc:description: 16 Spitfire MKIV's with all the original colors proposed by Triumph when new. From left to right and top to bottom: White, Wedgwood Blue (up to January 1972), Laurel Green (up to January 1972), Sapphire Blue, Signal Red (up to January 1972), Valencia Blue (up to January 1972), Saffron Yellow (up to September 1972), Damson Red (up to September 1972), Sienna Brown, Pimento Red (from January 1972 on), Emerald Green (from January 1972 on), Carmine red (from September 1972 on), Mallard Green (from September 1972 on), French Blue (from September 1972 on), Mimosa Yellow (from February 1973 on), Magenta (from February 1973 on).
